```C# Snippet:PlaywrightWorkspace_CreateOrUpdate
```
```

### Update a workspace to enable reporting and set storage URI

```C# Snippet:PlaywrightWorkspace_UpdateReportingAndStorage
```
```

### Configure managed identity on a workspace

```C# Snippet:PlaywrightWorkspace_ConfigureIdentity
```
```

For more samples, see the [.NET Management Library Code Samples](https://aka.ms/azuresdk-net-mgmt-samples).
```

Replace the **Next steps** section:

```markdown
## Next steps

For more information about Microsoft Azure SDK, see [this website](https://azure.github.io/azure-sdk/).
```

with:

```markdown
